summary: This is a retexture for Skyrim where the original textures have been run through the Deepdream neural network.
descriptionHtml:
To install extract the textures folder and place it in your Skyrim Data folder
(For example the location for Steam is C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Skyrim\Data)

Note that this is only for the original Skyrim and does not include any of the DLCs.


This mod was created with googles deepream Neural Network
https://github.com/google/deepdream
author: Jam2go

files.name: DeepDreamRetexture.rar
files.changelogHtml: Retextures most of the original game (a few are missing). UI and FX textures for the most part haven't been retextured
